rows.label: qst202301_0010
rows.name:
Yaegiri called us here, but
she's nowhere to be seen...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202301_0020
rows.name: We got the time right, didn't we?

rows.label: qst202301_0030
rows.name: There should be no issue.

rows.label: qst202301_0040
rows.name:
She probably overslept
and is running late, mo.

rows.label: qst202301_0050
rows.name: Hah, made it just in time!

rows.label: qst202301_0060
rows.name: You didn't make it just in time, mo.

rows.label: qst202301_0070
rows.name: Oh, whoops, my bad. Guess I'm late.

rows.label: qst202301_0080
rows.name:
On the way here, I spotted a real
tough-looking monster, you see.

rows.label: qst202301_0090
rows.name:
I guess I lost track of
time while fighting it.

rows.label: qst202301_0100
rows.name: Same old battle-crazed you, I see...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202301_0110
rows.name: You know it.

rows.label: qst202301_0120
rows.name:
So, what did you want
to talk to us about?

rows.label: qst202301_0130
rows.name: Right. I want to file a complaint.

rows.label: qst202301_0140
rows.name:
You all know very well how
much I love fighting strong
opponents, right?

rows.label: qst202301_0150
rows.name:
And I'm grateful that you've been
passing missions my way where I
might run into some tough guys.

rows.label: qst202301_0160
rows.name: But that's the problem?

rows.label: qst202301_0170
rows.name: Exactly.

rows.label: qst202301_0180
rows.name: They're all a total cakewalk!

rows.label: qst202301_0190
rows.name:
In the end, there aren't any of the
strong opponents I'm looking for, so
I can't get a single decent fight!

rows.label: qst202301_0200
rows.name: I want a tense, life-or-death battle,

rows.label: qst202301_0210
rows.name:
but all I get are fights
I could win in my sleep!

rows.label: qst202301_0220
rows.name:
So, you want us to let you
fight someone stronger?

rows.label: qst202301_0230
rows.name: That's the idea.

rows.label: qst202301_0240
rows.name:
At this rate, I'm going to get
so frustrated I'll either go on
a rampage or rot from boredom!

rows.label: qst202301_0250
rows.name:
But, there aren't many
opponents strong enough
to satisfy you, Yaegiri...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202301_0260
rows.name:
Well, we have Homura and
Hikari right here, don't we?

rows.label: qst202301_0270
rows.name: N-No, that's a bit much, even for you.

rows.label: qst202301_0280
rows.name: Yeah, probably.

rows.label: qst202301_0290
rows.name:
That's why I'm saying we should
go look for one together!

rows.label: qst202301_0300
rows.name: Alst is a big place...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202301_0310
rows.name:
So there's got to be one or
two opponents out there who
can make me get serious,

rows.label: qst202301_0320
rows.name:
one or two monsters
somewhere, don't you think?

rows.label: qst202301_0330
rows.name:
If you don't find one, my
frustration is going to explode!

rows.label: qst202301_0340
rows.name:
I might start attacking Kagutsuchi,
Saika, Byakko, or Hana!

rows.label: qst202301_0350
rows.name: Mo mo mo!

rows.label: qst202301_0360
rows.name: Okay, okay! Let's all look for one!

rows.label: qst202301_0370
rows.name:
Understood. That too
is a Driver's duty.

rows.label: qst202301_0380
rows.name:
Yeah. It'd be a problem if
she actually rampaged.

rows.label: qst202301_0390
rows.name: Honestly, what a handful.

rows.label: qst202301_0400
rows.name: Thanks, everyone!

rows.label: qst202301_0410
rows.name: Now, let's go find a real tough one!
